Colorize your code for posting to blogs. Uses the CodeRay gem for the heavy lifting.
Simple but effective layout, just paste your original code and click on the Colorize
tab to see the result. Use the HTML tab to copy the HTML source.

Sinatra-based, run it with e.g. Thin:

  rackup -s thin furtacor.ru


